text:
🏋️An Adult Fitness Corner located right at the end of the Park beside Clementi Road.
🏋️The exercise equipments were anchored on rubberized floor within a circular space, with rest benches flanked around the circumference.
🏋️Basic exercise equipments that includes Monkey Bar, Chin-up Bar, Parallel Bar, Push-up Bars, Sit-up Benches and Balancing Beams.
